OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FStaying mostly cloudy overnight with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain, but these mostly in
OL,9,Fthe west with clearer spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping in the east. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FOccasional brighter spells by
OL,13,Fday with only a few light showers
OL,14,Fappearing. Showers becoming heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes in the evening and may form
OL,16,Flonger spells of rain. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
